HEADWORD: Taglia
<hw>Tagl"ia</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[It., a cutting, a
pulley, from <ets>tagliare</ets> to cut. See <er>Tailor</er>.]</ety>
